Title: Establishes real property tax abatement for the value of land used for replanting or crop expansion of woody biomass used for the production of ethanol or biofuels
Summary: Establishes a real property tax abatement for the value of land used for replanting or crop expansion of woody biomass used for the production of ethanol or biodiesel, including willow.
LawCode: Amd ยง305, Ag & Mkts L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law, in relation to establishing a real property tax abatement for the owners of land used for replanting or crop expansion of woody biomass for the production of ethanol or biofuels, including willow
